{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|anatomy}} The region back of the [[knee]] [[joint]]; the [[popliteal]] space; the [[hock]].
# {{lb|en|countable}} A [[thigh]] and [[buttock]] of an animal slaughtered for meat.
# {{lb|en|uncountable}} Meat from the thigh of a [[hog]] cured for food.
